select s.school_id,m.school_name,s.cluster_id,c.cluster_name,s.block_id,b.block_name,s.district_id,d.district_name from school_geo_master as s left join school_master as m on m.school_id=s.school_id left join cluster_tmp as c on s.cluster_id=c.cluster_id left join block_tmp as b on s.block_id=b.block_id left join district_tmp as d on s.district_id=d.district_id

update school_geo_master as b set cluster_latitude=a.cluster_latitude, cluster_longitude=a.cluster_longitude, updated_on=now() from (select cluster_id,percentile_disc(0.5) within group (order by school_latitude) as cluster_latitude, percentile_disc(0.5) within group (order by school_longitude) as cluster_longitude from school_geo_master group by cluster_id) as a where a.cluster_id=b.cluster_id
